---
servings: 4
---

Thoroughly drain the @tuna{400%g} and place in a #large bowl{}.

Add @celery{3%tsp}(finely chopped) and @red onion{2%tbsp}(finely chopped, soaked in water), @pickle relish{2%tbsp}, @parsley{2%tbsp}(finely chopped), @mayo{1/3%cup}, @mustard{1%tsp}, @lemon juice{1%tbsp}, @olive oil{1%tsp}, and @salt{1/4%tsp}/@pepper{1/8%tsp} to taste.

Stir to combine and enjoy immediately.